tasks: Use advanced mathematical and computer science skills to analyze vast pools of data under the guidance of more senior data scientists.
Communicate clearly and effectively with both clients and multi-disciplinary teams.
Search for patterns in data that can provide solutions to business problems or create new business opportunities.
